name: Natural Vitamin Boost Serum 1oz
description: Formulated to brighten, soothe, hydrate, and replenish the skin with Vitamin C, B3, and B5. Suitable for all skin types, especially mature skin. Ingredients: Aqua, Glycerin, 3-O-Ethyl Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C), Niacinamide (Vitamin B3), Panthenol (Vitamin B5), 1,2-Hexanediol, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Citrate, Sodium Phytate, Polysorbate-20, Citric Acid
